table.name: ob_ship_unit
table.description: The details for a base order can be either specified by the line item (OB_LINE and related tables) or by the shipping units. The shipping units include the specification of pallets or packaging information. The shipper may not know or may choose not to specify the contents within the palettes. Other information like weight, height, pickup times etc. may be specified.

columns.name: OB_SHIP_UNIT_GID
columns.description: The GID for the ship unit associated to an order base.

columns.name: OB_SHIP_UNIT_XID
columns.description: The XID for the ship unit associated to a order base.

columns.name: ORDER_BASE_GID
columns.description: The order release associated to this ship unit.

columns.name: TRANSPORT_HANDLING_UNIT_GID
columns.description: The transport handling unit identifier defined for the ship unit. Examples are a box and a pallet.

columns.name: SHIP_UNIT_COUNT
columns.description: The number of ship units this entry represents. Ship unit count of 1 to model discrete ship units and bulk orders. Greater than 1 to model multiple uniform ship units.

columns.name: SOURCE_LOCATION_GID
columns.description: The source location GID for the pickup location associated with this order base ship unit.

columns.name: DEST_LOCATION_GID
columns.description: The destination location GID for the delivery location associated with this order base ship unit.

columns.name: EARLY_PICKUP_DATE
columns.description: The earliest date when the item can be picked up.

columns.name: LATE_PICKUP_DATE
columns.description: The latest date when the item can be picked up.

columns.name: EARLY_DELIVERY_DATE
columns.description: The earliest date when the item can be delivered.

columns.name: LATE_DELIVERY_DATE
columns.description: The latest date when the item can be picked delivered.

columns.name: WEIGHT
columns.description: The gross weight of the ship unit, the sum of the ship unit line contents weight plus the tare weight of the transport handling unit.

columns.name: WEIGHT_UOM_CODE
columns.description: The gross weight unit of measure.

columns.name: WEIGHT_BASE
columns.description: The gross weight in the base unit of measure.

columns.name: VOLUME
columns.description: The gross volume of the ship unit, the sum of the ship unit line contents volume plus the tare volume of the transport handling unit.

columns.name: VOLUME_UOM_CODE
columns.description: The gross volume unit of measure.

columns.name: VOLUME_BASE
columns.description: The gross volume in the base unit of measure.

columns.name: LENGTH
columns.description: The length of each order base ship unit. If this row represents 20 of the same ship units, the total length is 20 x unit length.

columns.name: LENGTH_UOM_CODE
columns.description: Unit of measure for the unit length column.

columns.name: LENGTH_BASE
columns.description: The unit length in base units.

columns.name: WIDTH
columns.description: The width of each order base ship unit. Each row may represent the ship unit count number of same ship units.

columns.name: WIDTH_UOM_CODE
columns.description: Unit of measure for the unit width.

columns.name: WIDTH_BASE
columns.description: The unit width in base units.

columns.name: HEIGHT
columns.description: The height of each order base ship unit. If this row represents the 20 same ship units, the total height is 20 x unit height.

columns.name: HEIGHT_UOM_CODE
columns.description: The unit of measure for unit height column.

columns.name: HEIGHT_BASE
columns.description: The unit height in base units.

columns.name: DECLARED_VALUE
columns.description: The declared value of the total of the goods, ship unit content lines on the ship unit.

columns.name: DECLARED_VALUE_BASE
columns.description: The declared value in the base currency.

columns.name: DECLARED_VALUE_CURRENCY_GID
columns.description: The declared value currency identifier.

columns.name: FLEX_COMMODITY_CODE
columns.description: The user defined commodity code for the item. E.g.. HTS, SITC, STCC, NMFC

columns.name: FLEX_COMMODITY_QUAL_GID
columns.description: The user defined commodity qualifier identify the type of commodity classification being used, such as NMFC.

columns.name: PLAN_FROM_LOCATION_GID
columns.description: The plan from location GID can define a location other than the source location of the ship unit for OTM to beginning planning transport.

columns.name: PLAN_TO_LOCATION_GID
columns.description: The plan from location GID can define a location other than the source location of the ship unit for OTM to beginning planning transport.

columns.name: NET_WEIGHT
columns.description: The total net weight of the ship unit content lines on the ship unit.

columns.name: NET_WEIGHT_UOM_CODE
columns.description: The net weight unit of measure.

columns.name: NET_WEIGHT_BASE
columns.description: The net weight in the base unit of measure.

columns.name: NET_VOLUME
columns.description: The total net volume of the ship unit content lines on the ship unit.

columns.name: NET_VOLUME_UOM_CODE
columns.description: The net volume unit of measure.

columns.name: NET_VOLUME_BASE
columns.description: The net volume in the base unit of measure.

columns.name: IS_SHIPPABLE
columns.description: A Y/N indicator defining if the order base line is ready to be shipped by creating an order release for it.

columns.name: RELEASED_COUNT
columns.description: The number of ship units that have been processed onto order release through the releasing logic.

columns.name: LOAD_POINT
columns.description: The specific loading location for the source location on the ship unit.

columns.name: UNLOAD_POINT
columns.description: The specific unloading location for the delivery location on the ship unit.

columns.name: PICKUP_IS_APPT
columns.description: Indicates if the early/late pickup times are appointment times

columns.name: DELIVERY_IS_APPT
columns.description: Indicates if the early/late delivery times are appointment times

columns.name: PLAN_FROM_LOAD_POINT
columns.description: The specific loading location for the plan from location on the ship unit.

columns.name: PLAN_TO_UNLOAD_POINT
columns.description: The specific unloading location for the plan to location on the ship unit.

columns.name: TAG_1
columns.description: Additional information about the item. Like the color or size code, etc.

columns.name: TAG_2
columns.description: Additional information about the item. Like the color or size code, etc.

columns.name: TAG_3
columns.description: Additional information about the item. Like the color or size code, etc.

columns.name: TAG_4
columns.description: Additional information about the item. Like the color or size code, etc.

columns.name: CORE_DIAMETER
columns.description: For cylindrical objects, this defines the diameter of the core.

columns.name: CORE_DIAMETER_UOM_CODE
columns.description: The unit of measure for the diameter of the core.

columns.name: CORE_DIAMETER_BASE
columns.description: The diameter of the core in the base unit of measure.

columns.name: DIAMETER
columns.description: The unit diameter of the ship unit.

columns.name: DIAMETER_UOM_CODE
columns.description: Unit of measure for the unit diameter.

columns.name: DIAMETER_BASE
columns.description: The unit diameter in the base unit of measure.

columns.name: BUFFER_LOCATION_GID
columns.description: The buffer location to identify if this order base ship unit is being modeled with a buffer location to hold inventory prior to final delivery.

columns.name: DOMAIN_NAME
columns.description: Database domain where this data is stored.

columns.name: INSERT_USER
columns.description: The user ID of the data insert user.

columns.name: INSERT_DATE
columns.description: Date and time of data insert.

columns.name: UPDATE_USER
columns.description: The user ID of the data update user.

columns.name: UPDATE_DATE
columns.description: Date and time of the most recent data update.

columns.name: LOAD_CONFIG_SETUP_GID
columns.description: A load configurator set up identifier to be used by the load configuration engine as the input rules for how the ship unit was built.

columns.name: SPLITTABLE_BY
columns.description: Indicates how the resulting order release ship unit may be split across equipment.
